  (text "Reviewed FB-100 value-bearing schematic inputs:\n- JFB1 24-pin interface with USB_D_P, USB_D_N, USB_CC1, USB_CC2, USB_VBUS_SENSE, FB_3V3_IO, GND, status RGB, CH_LED_1..CH_LED_10, SERVICE_BTN, RESET_BTN, OLED_SCL, OLED_SDA.\n- USB-C service is device-only; CC Rd behavior; ESD protection; VBUS sense-only; no back-power into LB-100 or PB-100.\n- USB/no-back-power layout model is closed; ESD placement, D+/D- routing, CC behavior, VBUS sense-only routing, shield return, and JFB1 FFC transition are layout inputs.\n- footprint binding is closed in FB100.pretty but schematic symbol promotion remains open.\n- UI hardware stays role-free: channel/status indicators only, no accessory names.\n- Optional OLED remains DNP unless populated by reviewed variant.\n- Mechanical envelope, USB access, LED/button alignment, service sealing, and enclosure boundary are reviewed."
